  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Way Of Heaven
---
Shih Ch'eng-ch'i backed respectfully away so that he would not tread on
Lao Tzu's shadow, and then advanced once more in humble manner and
asked how he should go about cultivating his person.
